File-Split version 0.30
=======================

To install this module, install through

	cpan File::Split

There are dependancies on:

	Data::Dumper;
	File::Basename

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

        Data::Dumper;
        File::Basename
        Array::Dissect

